Contents :

/macros
ToyStoppedHSCP.C
Contains all the code to setup and run the toy MC.

RunMany*.C
Macros containing experiment parameters

*Plots.C
Macros that just make the plots (having run appropriate RunMany*.C)

Style.C
Plot style macro


Instructions :

cvs co -d StoppedHSCP/ToyMC UserCode/StoppedHSCP/ToyMC
cd StoppedHSCP/ToyMC
eval `scramv1 ru -sh` (if you're on lxplus)
root


To make all the plots from ROOT prompt :

.L macros/ToyStoppedHSCP.C
.X macros/Style.C
.X macros/RunMany.C
.X macros/TimePlots.C
.X macros/MassPlots.C
.X macros/RunMany_NeutralinoScan.C
.X macros/NeutralinoPlots.C
.X macros/RunMany_Uncertainty.C
.X macros/TimePlots_Uncertainty.C

